on CentOS environment.

Prerequisites:
--------------

| Title                           | Description                                                                                                                            |
|---------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| CentOS Image                    | 7 or 8                                                                                                                                 |
| contentserver_docker_ubuntu.tar | <https://mimage.opentext.com/support/ecm/secure/software/dell/documentum/documentumcontentserver/16.4/contentserver_docker_ubuntu.tar> |
